Hi Antonia,

This works just fine for me:

yi <- c(.23, .55, .33)
sei <- rep(.1, 3)
ci.lb <- yi - 1.96*sei
ci.ub <- yi + 1.96*sei
forest(yi, ci.lb=ci.lb, ci.ub=ci.ub, showweights=TRUE, alim=c(0,1), refline=NA)

Best,
Wolfgang

